Welcome to JW Broadcasting. On our program for this month, we'll hear the

00:00:08.349 --> 00:00:13.390
experience of Brother Jim Brown. He studied the Bible with Jehovah's Witnesses

00:00:13.390 --> 00:00:19.710
off and on for 30 years. What motivated him to make changes and dedicate his

00:00:19.710 --> 00:00:24.350
life to Jehovah? It's important for youth to develop good spiritual habits

00:00:24.350 --> 00:00:30.309
early. How can teenagers get the most out of their daily Bible reading? We have

