00:01:05.099 --> 00:01:11.540
just such a story. Meet Jim Brown, a brother from Key Largo, Florida in the

00:01:11.540 --> 00:01:17.060
United States. Before becoming one of Jehovah's Witnesses, he was on a dangerous

00:01:17.060 --> 00:01:22.659
path of vice and violence. What changes did he have to make on the road to true

00:01:22.659 --> 00:01:36.659
worship? 53 years old. I was known as a troublemaker. I was fighting in the

00:01:36.659 --> 00:01:43.900
bars, come to a point where you began to enjoy it. He was flat out scary. He was a

00:01:43.900 --> 00:01:50.420
very mean and violent man. So everybody kind of kept their distance from him. My

00:01:50.420 --> 00:01:57.140
language was too testable. I would make grown men blush by the things that I

00:01:57.140 --> 00:02:02.659
could say and things that I would do. It was involved with some bikers and they

00:02:02.659 --> 00:02:07.939
were trying to prospect me into getting into their club. Things were escalating.

00:02:07.939 --> 00:02:15.340
We got married very young and we were 17. And had my oldest daughter? I was the

00:02:15.340 --> 00:02:22.939
mom and he lived a life of being out with his friends and partying.

00:02:22.939 --> 00:02:26.780
About that time, my wife started studying a Bible which Jehovah's Witnesses. It was a

00:02:26.780 --> 00:02:32.819
big change for her. But she explained the reason behind it. I couldn't argue with it.

00:02:32.819 --> 00:02:40.300
She talked me into studying. I studied from 28 years old to 30. I always

00:02:40.300 --> 00:02:44.979
seen it. I always seen it. I know this is where I needed to be. Somehow I just

00:02:44.979 --> 00:02:49.539
could never break free of the person that I was. My mom always raised us in the

00:02:49.539 --> 00:02:54.900
truth growing up and that's what we knew. So then to see my dad where he was so

00:02:54.900 --> 00:03:01.099
different but yet believed it to be the truth. And then to see that his lifestyle

00:03:01.099 --> 00:03:07.020
didn't do him any good was kind of a good example of a bad example if that

00:03:07.020 --> 00:03:15.469
makes sense. I was afraid of the change. People accepted me for who I was. Being

00:03:15.469 --> 00:03:21.830
a tough guy. Being Jimmy Brown. The scripture comes to mind. I planted a

